    "contract_number": "00000000000000000000000041951",
    "summary": "This Contract (\"this Contract\"), entered into by and between Indiana Family and Social Services Administration, Division of Mental Health and Addiction (the \"State\") and HEALTH AND HOSPITAL CORPORATION OF MARION COUNTY DBA SANDRA ESKENAZI MENTAL HEALTH CENTER (the \"Contractor\"), is executed pursuant to the terms and conditions set forth herein. In consideration of those mutual undertakings and covenants, the parties agree as follows:",
