      {
        "title": "1. Duties of Contractor.",
        "content": "The Contractor shall provide a Continuum of Care, including treatment and other services, to its eligible population. A detailed list of duties is set forth in Exhibit 1, 2, 3, 4, and 6 attached hereto and incorporated herein."
